133
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:43,680
Here.

134
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:45,920
It's okay. Come on.

135
00:09:50,960 --> 00:09:52,680
Sir, please drive faster.

136
00:09:52,760 --> 00:09:53,600
Okay.

137
00:09:54,160 --> 00:09:56,160
- It hurts.
- Sir, please hurry.

138
00:09:56,240 --> 00:09:57,120
Faster, okay?

139
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:58,600
- Okay.
- We're almost there.

140
