for appendicitis.

165
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:17,240
It's a little expensive,
but all surgeries involve risks.

166
00:11:17,320 --> 00:11:18,600
Even minimally invasive surgery?

167
00:11:18,680 --> 00:11:20,200
