caused by stomach flu.

208
00:15:37,120 --> 00:15:38,080
Here.

209
00:15:38,840 --> 00:15:39,800
I can feed myself.

210
00:15:44,160 --> 00:15:46,400
Just behave and eat, wounded comrade.

211
00:15:56,080 --> 00:15:57,040
