so that I can sign off as your boyfriend.

220
00:16:28,880 --> 00:16:30,960
If you deny it now,

221
00:16:31,040 --> 00:16:32,760
I'll bear legal liabilities.

222
00:16:40,000 --> 00:16:41,080
Miss.

223
00:16:41,160 --> 00:16:43,160
